Pumpkin pie from the Libby's pumpkin pure can

Preheat oven 425

1 (15 ounce) can pumpkin puree
1 (14 ounce) can evaporated milk
3/4 Cup sugar
1/2 tsp salt
1 tsp ground cinnamon
1/2 tsp ground ginger
1/4 tsp ground cloves
2 eggs
1 9" unbaked pie crust.

Mix up dry stuff in small bowl.
Beat eggs in big bowl.
Stir pumpkin and dry stuff into big bowl.
Preheat oven 425.

Bake 425 - 15 min
Bake 350 - 30..40 min ('Till knife comes out clean 1" from edge.)

